data.title: Emptying and Filling the Tank for iRobot® Braava jet™ Mopping Robot
data.description: This is an instructional video for emptying and filling the Braava jet™ tank for the iRobot® Braava jet™ Mopping Robot. If using Wet Mopping or Damp Sweeping cleaning pads, Braava jet™ needs to be filled with water. Do not use any other cleaning solution with your robot other than water. Lift the handle to find the tank cap. Lift and swivel the cap to open. Tilt Braava jet™ upward and fill the tank to the top with warm water. Close the cap and lower the handle before starting.
